# Documentation site toolchain (Material for MkDocs + versioning).
# Top-level pins; Renovate keeps them current. The fully-resolved,
# hash-pinned lockfile is docs/requirements.txt (generated via:
#   pip-compile --generate-hashes docs/requirements.in
# ). CI installs it with `pip install --require-hashes` so every
# dependency — including transitive ones — is verified by hash
# (OpenSSF Scorecard Pinned-Dependencies).
